---
import Section from "@/components/Section.astro";
---

<Section title="About me">
  <div class="text-[0.95rem] font-light leading-relaxed sm:text-[1.05rem]">
    Hello there! I'm Carlos Tocino (Charlie Bacon for non-Spanish speakers), a
    software engineer based in Spain. I've basically been living inside a
    computer since I was a kid, coding for over 15 years and working
    professionally as a software engineer for more than 8. I currently work at <a
      class="accent-link"
      href="https://radancy.com"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer">Radancy</a
    > as technical team lead.
    <br />
    <br />
    Using Rust 🦀 on a daily basis, at work and for fun.
    <br />
    <br />
    I use neovim, btw.
    <br />
    <br />
    I'm also a vinyl collector; you can check my humble list of records on <a
      class="accent-link"
      href="https://www.discogs.com/es/user/SharliBeicon/collection"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noreferrer"
    >
      Discogs</a
    >.
  </div>
</Section>
